<HEADLINE> Chinese Foreign Affairs and Trade Ministers Return to Beijing </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 14 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Foreign Minister Tang
Jiaxuan and Minister of Foreign Trade and Economic Cooperation Shi
Guangsheng returned to Beijing tonight after attending the 11th
APEC (Asia Pacific Economic Cooperation) ministerial meeting in
Auckland, New Zealand. 
</P>
