</P>
<P>
-- The 22nd Universal Postal Union Congress, which has been
focusing on critical reforms for postal systems worldwide, will
end today. An announcement is expected to be made by its hosts
detailing the "Beijing Postal Strategy," a plan intended to lead
the industry into the next millennium.
</P>
<P>
