investment in Vietnam both slipped in the first eight months of
1999, said the latest issue of Vietnam Investment Review.
</P>
<P>
Vietnam's export volume to the United States from the beginning
of the year to the end of August totaled just 250 million U.S.
dollars, according to Vietnam's customs statistics. (Vietnam-US
Investment) 
