<HEADLINE> HK Kicks off New Asian Expo on Industrial Technology </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, September 15 (Xinhua) -- Over 200 manufacturers and
suppliers coming from 10 countries and regions today gathered at
the Asian Industrial Exhibition '99 to demonstrate a full range of
latest industrial technology in the region.
</P>
<P>
The exhibition, which is held at the Hong Kong Convention and
Exhibition Center from September 15 to 18, is one of the most
comprehensive industrial events in Asia.
</P>
<P>
"Acting as an open door to the most innovative technologies and
equipment, the Asian Industrial Exhibition is held annually with
an aim to facilitate the technological development of Hong Kong
industry," said Henry Tang, chairman of Business &AMP; Industrial
Trade Fairs Ltd., at the opening ceremony.
</P>
<P>
On display are machine tools, metalworking machinery, special
purpose machinery, packing and printing equipment, parts and
supplies, plastics processing and testing equipment.
</P>
<P>
Held concurrently will be a seminar of "astounding mold and die
manufacturing system", introducing the trend of control system in
machining center and the difference between vertical and
horizontal machining center in mold and die manufacturing
application.  
