<HEADLINE> France to Send 500 Soldiers to East Timor </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, September 15 (Xinhua) -- France will send 500 troops to
join the United Nations peacekeeping force in East Timor, Agence
France-Presse quoted a source of the Elysee presidential palace as
saying Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
