overseas territories in the South Pacific like New Caledonia,
where the local Kanak people are of the same ethnic origin of
Timorese.
</P>
<P>
Some Kanak nationalist groups have appealed to the French
government to intervene with Indonesia to stop the violence in
East Timor. 
